data.description: Lovely, Solid brick ranch situated on a combined .72 acre wooded lot with panoramic views of the river. The welcoming covered front porch leads to the delightful kitchen that opens to the eating area with Hardwood floors, plaster walls and large windows. The LR offers plaster walls, HW floors, a raised hearth brick, decorative fireplace, picture window & glass door leading to the upper-level balcony.  The 1st level also features 2 bedrooms with generous closets, lighting ceiling fans, HW floors & a hall bath with charming claw foot tub. The finished lower level offers space for a possible third 17x11 bedroom & additional 10x10 flex/home office with laminate flooring & brick accented, decorative wood stove, large windows and door leading to the covered side porch. LL family room with kitchenette area and beamed ceilings, floor to ceiling glass windows. LL also offers a full bath with large, tiled shower & sizable laundry room. New Furnace, AC and Roof in 2021. New Hot Water Tank 2019.
